"snippet" : "FB-specific error codes DiagCode Statue Name Status description and output setting 16#C000 Parameter Error Invalid value of the TestTime parameter Values between 0 ms and 150 ms are possible. Ready = TRUE S_OSSD_Out = FALSE S_TestOut = TRUE TestPossible = FALSE TestExecuted = FALSE Error = TRUE 16#C...", 
